------------------------------------------------------------------------------
With a pipe, a special modifier can be applied to a value. A few of them are
supporting arguments, they can be appended via a comma or as function arguments.
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
{{ a     | json }}
{{b|hex|rot13}}
{{c|encode}}
{{d|md5}}
{{d|hash("whirlpool")|cut(10)}}
